ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 252, British Columbia
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 252 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of federal concern; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to BRITISH COLUMBIA with respect to the interface fires that occurred from June 30 to September 27, 2022.
